snippet.title: [A game by meaka] Haze's Hectic Halloween Happenstance Playthrough
snippet.description:
Game Link: https://meaka.itch.io/hazes-hectic-halloween-happenstance

Haze's Hectic Halloween Happenstance Playthrough is an RPG Maker game where a "demon" fails at their job.

Overall, not a bad game. It's alright. But maybe I'll give their other games a chance. The humor is kinda good at least. Maybe I'll check their other games sometime

Anyway, I hope you enjoy!
